<DIV1>
<PB REF="1310">
<HEAD>THE HISTORY OF ENGLAND.</HEAD>
<DIV2>
<HEAD>FOURTH BOOK.</HEAD>
<HEAD TYPE="sub">From the Death of king EDWARD III. to the Union of the Two Ro&s;es, in the per&s;on of HENRY VII.</HEAD>
<DIV3 N="1" TYPE="chapter">
