<DIV4 N="1" TYPE="section">
<HEAD>&sect; I.</HEAD>
<P>DURING the interval between the parliament which depo&s;ed Ri|chard, and that which was convoked by his &s;ucce&s;&s;or, this prince filled $ome places that were either vacant, or occupied by per&s;ons who were not agreeable to his inclinations and de&s;igns. The $arl of Northumberland was
