<PB N="214" REF="2160">
L$$$a&s;t$r by an auth$nt$c act; and Henry indulged with a con&s;iderable &s;ub|&s;$d$ on wo$l, be&s;i$$s the remainder of what had been granted to Richa$d; $$rt of which was not yet lev$ed. A$ter the&s;e conce&s;&s;ions, Henry could do $o le$s than p$b$$&s;h a general amne&s;ty: from which, however, he except$d $word$ $word$ $f the d$ke of Glouce&s;ter; one of whom b$ing apprehended, $word$ $$e particulars o$ the murder, as they have been already related. He $word$ death at London, and his head b$ing &s;ent to Calais, was fixed<NOTE PLACE="marg">$line$</NOTE> ov$r one of the gates of the city.</P>
